    <item>
      <title>1.0.7</title>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 May 2026 14:54:59 +0000</pubDate>
      <sparkle:version>7</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.0.7</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[<h2 id="whats-new">What's new</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>First-run onboarding flow</strong>: a guided welcome +
preview sheet now greets new users on first launch, importing existing
entries from <code>/etc/hosts</code> into a starter profile so nothing
is lost when the app takes over the managed block.</li>
<li><strong>JSON import help</strong>: in-app help button on the
Settings JSON importer describes the expected schema and points to a
working example.</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="improvements">Improvements</h2>
<ul>
<li><code>HostsFileManager</code> / <code>HostsFileParser</code> /
<code>SystemHostEntries</code> now share a single parser for the system
file, used both by the onboarding preview and the live managed-block
writer.</li>
<li>New <code>Scripts/full-release.sh</code> orchestrates the whole
release flow (preflight → bump → build → publish draft → tag + push) in
one command; <code>docs/release.md</code> updated accordingly.</li>
<li>README refreshed.</li>
</ul>]]></description>
